nfants." J Pediatr 114 (1989): 847-52[18] Kaka JS, Lyman C, Kilarski DJ "Tobramycin-furosemide interaction." Drug Intell Clin Pharm 18 (1984): 235-8[19] Mathog RH, Klein WJ "Ototoxicity of ethacrynic acid and aminoglycoside antibiotics in uremia." N Engl J Med 280 (1969): 1223-4', 1767365209);
